divs: Sighting DetailsI was camping at Bennington Lake around midnight. Sitting outside, we were watching the stars. I noticed movenemt in the sky with two stars traveling almost parrallel to each other. A third object approached and the ground where we were sitting and it looked more like an orb than a star.
